data.description: Nestled in the heart of Red Oak, Texas, this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover an expansive floor plan boasting 2 living rooms downstairs and a spacious kitchen equipped with top-of-the-line appliances. With 1782 sq ft of living space spread across 2 floors, this property is ideal for family living. Outside, the large backyard provides an inviting space for outdoor relaxation. Priced at $325,000, this residence promises the quintessential suburban lifestyle with modern conveniences.
